# Design Workflow - Adam's Cognitive Profile

## The Core Insight

**Cognitive Profile:**
- Structural Visualization: 5th percentile — does not naturally see spatial relationships
- Analytical Reasoning: 13th percentile — sequential organization doesn't come naturally

**Strengths:**
- Pattern recognition
- Strategic "why" thinking
- Numerical reasoning
- Taste (knows it when he sees it)

## Your Job as an AI

**Translate spatial decisions into strategic questions.**

When Adam hits a design block:
- DON'T ask "what padding?" or "should this be 16px or 24px?"
- DO ask "what's most important here?" or "what should the user see first?"

He has taste but not spatial intuition. Help him use references and frameworks instead of trying to visualize.

