## Framework 2: Constraint Scales

Never freestyle. Pick from these fixed values:

### Spacing (padding, margins, gaps)
```
4px   → Tight (between related items)
8px   → Compact (chip padding, small gaps)
12px  → Default small (list items)
16px  → Default medium (section padding)
24px  → Comfortable (card padding)
32px  → Roomy (section gaps)
48px  → Dramatic (major section breaks)
```

### Font Sizes
```
12px  → Fine print, metadata, timestamps
14px  → Body text, descriptions
16px  → Default UI text, buttons
18px  → Emphasized body, subheadings
24px  → Section headings
32px  → Page titles
48px  → Hero headlines
```

### Font Weight
```
400   → Normal (body text)
500   → Medium (subtle emphasis)
600   → Semibold (buttons, labels)
700   → Bold (headings, strong emphasis)
```

### Border Radius
```
4px   → Subtle softening (inputs, small buttons)
8px   → Standard rounded (cards, chips)
12px  → Friendly rounded (modals, large cards)
9999px → Pill shape (tags, badges)
```

### Opacity (for muting)
```
100%  → Full prominence
70%   → Slightly muted
50%   → Secondary info
30%   → Disabled/hint
```

### Z-Index
```
0     → Default
10    → Dropdowns, tooltips
20    → Sticky headers
30    → Modals, overlays
40    → Toasts, notifications
```

