## Framework 3: The Feel → Reference → Constraints Pattern

When you can't decide, use this prompt template for Cursor:

```
I want [ELEMENT] to feel [ADJECTIVE].

Reference: [SCREENSHOT OR APP NAME]

Constraints:
- Spacing: use 8/16/24px scale
- Colors: [YOUR PALETTE or "match existing"]
- Match the visual weight of [REFERENCE]
```

### Feel Vocabulary
| If you want... | Say it feels... |
|----------------|-----------------|
| Easy to scan | Glanceable |
| Important | Prominent, bold |
| Secondary | Muted, subtle |
| Clickable | Tappable, interactive |
| Organized | Structured, grouped |
| Calm | Quiet, minimal |
| Energetic | Punchy, vibrant |
| Professional | Polished, clean |
| Friendly | Warm, approachable |

