## Framework 4: Common Patterns (Pick, Don't Invent)

### Cards
- Padding: 16px or 24px
- Border-radius: 8px or 12px
- Background: slightly lighter/darker than page
- Shadow: subtle or none for dark mode

### Chips/Tags
- Padding: 4px 8px or 6px 12px
- Border-radius: 9999px (pill) or 6px (rounded)
- Font size: 12px or 14px
- Selected: filled background
- Unselected: outline or ghost

### Buttons
- Primary: filled, brand color, 600 weight text
- Secondary: outline or ghost, muted color
- Padding: 8px 16px (small) or 12px 24px (default)
- Border-radius: match your chips

### Input Fields
- Height: 40px or 44px
- Padding: 8px 12px
- Border: 1px solid muted
- Border-radius: 6px or 8px
- Focus: brand color border

### Section Spacing
- Between related items: 8px or 12px
- Between groups: 24px
- Between sections: 32px or 48px

