## Framework 5: The "What's Wrong?" Diagnostic

When something looks off but you can't say why, run through this checklist:

| Symptom | Likely Fix |
|---------|------------|
| Feels cramped | Increase padding/margins by one scale step |
| Feels floaty | Decrease spacing, add borders or backgrounds |
| Can't find focus | Make one thing bigger, mute everything else |
| Looks chaotic | Align things, reduce variation |
| Feels cheap | Check font weights, add subtle shadows, refine spacing |
| Feels heavy | Reduce font weights, increase whitespace |
| Hard to read | Increase contrast, check font size |

