## Emergency Prompt Templates

### "I don't know what spacing to use"
```
Make the spacing feel balanced. Use 8px for tight groupings, 
16px for standard padding, 24px between distinct sections. 
Show me the result.
```

### "I don't know if this should be above or below"
```
The user needs to see [X] first, then [Y]. 
Arrange them in that priority order.
```

### "This looks wrong but I don't know why"
```
Something feels off about [ELEMENT]. Compare it to [REFERENCE APP]. 
What's different? Fix it to match that feel.
```

### "I can't decide between two options"
```
Show me both versions side by side:
Option A: [description]
Option B: [description]
I'll pick based on what I see.
```

