## The Meta-Rule

**When stuck for more than 2 minutes on a design decision:**

1. Find a reference (screenshot something that works)
2. Point Cursor at it
3. Say "match this feel"
4. Move on

Your time is worth more than pixel-perfect decisions. Ship it, then refine based on how it feels in use.

